{"tid":2167924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"會員“魯班七號”（＃132525）正是被banned 會員大英帝國（P牌）真身 ? (2)","createTime":"2020-08-21T12:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T14:12:24.000Z","uid":56015,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ecc81492466c44c963f27e1f56fe88b071696ff","tid":2167924,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"會員&ldquo;魯班七號&rdquo;（＃132525）正是被banned 會員大英帝國（P牌）真身？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2015904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2015904</a><br />\n<br />\n被banned 會員大英帝國（P牌），又名<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">將軍澳天晉</span></span>（<span class=\"gold\">因其自爆自己住係或擁有天晉3B 而聞名</span>），曾經以其on9 小學雞作風聞名，係五毛界闖出一片天。<br />\n<br />\n當中又以<span class=\"gold\">改wiki 五毛定義，瘋狂洗版，copy &amp; paste 大法，同利用大英解密法</span>依d出位方法令佢五毛嘅名聲發揚光大，印象深刻<br />\n而最後依d行為當然令到佢俾admin ban鳩咗 or 禁言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（大家千祈唔好學佢咁on9呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n不過，似乎佢又不甘寂寞，疑似用佢嘅真身<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">「魯班七號」</span></span>將大英帝國依個被banned 會員嘅已故身影重影於我地眼前。<br />\n<br />\n點解我地會知道呢？<br />\n<br />\n有位心水清既手足，做左個詳盡兼具科學理論性既推測po。睇完之後，我相信連&ldquo;<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">大英哥</span></span>&rdquo;呢條<span class=\"red\">狡猾的五毛狗</span>亦將會百詞莫辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink在樓下"},{"pid":"1b0e2ba31cff13816d552b9238dcd44befd08914","tid":2167924,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">圖文並茂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">手足詳細解構魯班七號之潛行大英</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下topic同本文相似，但內容極之詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員 魯班七號 （#132525) = 被banned 會員大英帝國 （P牌）？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2012217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2012217</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb8df1c693aead24d661acebcda88b243d8b8aab","tid":2167924,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9e4a7dd66fbf7a805078baffb5f61fc5bf74e1","tid":2167924,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill